// 文章
### 新建文章
POST http://127.0.0.1:7001/api/article/create HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenResponese.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "test3",
  "introduce": "introduce1",
  "content": "content1",
  "view_count": 0,
  "type": "5e4775d68382061716a948b0"
}


### 获取文章列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:7001/api/article HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json


### 更新文章
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:7001/api/article/5e48bcbe4c68ab0c1bc57dee HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenResponese.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "12345678",
}


### 获取文章详情
GET http://127.0.0.1:7001/api/article/:id HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json


### 删除文章
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:7001/api/article/5e478b1cce67e41cd9303640 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenResponese.response.body.token}}



